SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[Active], [m].[ApprovalCount], [m].[Approved], [m].[Deleted], [m].[EmployeeNumber], [m].[EmploymentDate], [m].[HasPaidFee], [m].[Location], [m].[MemberType], [m].[PersonId], [m].[RegistrationDate], [m].[RetirementDate], [m].[Tag], [m].[UserId], [p].[Id], [p].[Address1], [p].[Address2], [p].[Country], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[DateCreated], [p].[DateOfBirth], [p].[Email], [p].[FirstName], [p].[LastModifiedBy], [p].[LastModifiedDate], [p].[LastName], [p].[MaritalStatus], [p].[MiddleName], [p].[MobileNumber], [p].[PersonalEmail], [p].[Sex], [p].[StateId], [p].[Title], [p].[WorkPhone]
FROM [Members] AS [m]
